1949;;Make Believe Ballroom;;American;;Joseph Santley;;Ruth Warrick, Ron Randell;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Make_Believe_Ballroom;;The film focuses on two carhops as they compete in a mystery record contest. John Reid, in the reference book Popular Pictures of the Hollywood 1940s, commented, "... this is one of those films which string together a musical melange through the excuse of a radio show."[1][self-published source]